            <text>爱媛38# 天府四川果冻橙 身材圆润 肤色深橙 果肉入口化渣 甜度高达14度以上 特优果5斤12个装</text>
            <text>￥59.90</text>
            <view class='ht-list-x-box-text-icon'>
              <image src='../../assets/img/add.png'></image>
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class='ht-list-x-box'>
          <view class='ht-list-x-box-image'>
            <view><image src='https://img.yzcdn.cn/upload_files/2018/10/31/FliGojw5FYO-mD3jpcRuGUFRogAs.jpg?imageView2/2/w/520/h/0/q/75/format/webp'></image></view>
          </view>
          <view class='ht-list-x-box-text'>
