          </view>
          <view class='ht-list-x-box-text'>
            <text>【现摘现发】四川蒲江黄心猕猴桃5斤包邮精品中果（单果70-90g） 新鲜爽口 清甜爆汁</text>
            <text>￥29.90</text>
            <view class='ht-list-x-box-text-icon'>
              <image src='../../assets/img/add.png'></image>
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class='ht-list-x-box'>
          <view class='ht-list-x-box-image'>
            <view><image src='https://img.yzcdn.cn/upload_files/2018/10/11/FopWmiJuXOKpV-qgwqcIZUwTpL7o.jpg?imageView2/2/w/520/h/0/q/75/format/webp'></image></view>
          </view>
          <view class='ht-list-x-box-text'>
            <text>金秋红蜜桃 甜度高达18度 230天成长期 秋冬晚熟 12个装</text>
            <text>￥88.00</text>
            <view class='ht-list-x-box-text-icon'>
              <image src='../../assets/img/add.png'></image>
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class='ht-list-x-box'>
          <view class='ht-list-x-box-image'>
            <view><image src='https://img.yzcdn.cn/upload_files/2018/10/25/FlR03uZsGPUXIlRi0tUUeAw_Y5Ty.jpg?imageView2/2/w/520/h/0/q/75/format/webp'></image></view>
          </view>
          <view class='ht-list-x-box-text'>
            <text>可以喝的爆汁橙 九月红宝宝橙 皮薄多汁 细腻化渣 酸甜爽口 自家果园橙子现摘现发 不打蜡4斤装包邮</text>
            <text>￥39.90</text>
            <view class='ht-list-x-box-text-icon'>
              <image src='../../assets/img/add.png'></image>
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class='ht-list-x-box'>
          <view class='ht-list-x-box-image'>
            <view><image src='https://img.yzcdn.cn/upload_files/2018/08/29/FpERFKjXX4EqTgogmIMMDt8zbjq7.jpg?imageView2/2/w/520/h/0/q/75/format/webp'></image></view>
          </view>
          <view class='ht-list-x-box-text'>
            <text>【中国猕猴桃之乡】大雨影响72小时内发货  好吃到爆的周至猕猴桃 助农装净重5斤 礼盒装徐香标准24枚 品质保证 汁液多，肉质细致果香味，酸甜可口</text>
            <text>￥29.90</text>
            <view class='ht-list-x-box-text-icon'>
              <image src='../../assets/img/add.png'></image>
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view class='ht-list-x-box'>
          <view class='ht-list-x-box-image'>
            <view><image src='https://img.yzcdn.cn/upload_files/2018/09/19/FoaapXqgqCGf_jUY5ieQPuIMw7fC.jpg?imageView2/2/w/520/h/0/q/75/format/webp'></image></view>
          </view>
          <view class='ht-list-x-box-text'>
            <text>「甜蜜脆爽」出口日本的甜柿子 柿子香味 苹果口感  入口脆甜可口 咔嚓脆！</text>
            <text>￥29.50</text>
            <view class='ht-list-x-box-text-icon'>
              <image src='../../assets/img/add.png'></image>
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>
    </scroll-view>
  </view>

  <view class='list-wrapper'>
    <view>
      <image src='https://img.yzcdn.cn/upload_files/2018/02/24/FjuVxU7yCUkaGBGwenPv-zTcHsm1.jpg?imageView2/2/w/730/h/0/q/75/format/webp'></image>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class='home-list'>
    <view class='home-list-x-box' bindtap='toDetail' data-id='{{item.id}}' wx:for="{{list}}" wx:key="{{item.id}}">
      <view class='home-list-x-box-image'>
        <view><image src='{{item.url}}'></image></view>
        </view>
        <view class='home-list-x-box-text'>
          <text>{{item.text}}</text>
          <text>￥{{item.money}}</text>
          <view class='home-list-x-box-text-icon'>
            <image src='../../assets/img/add.png'></image>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</scroll-view>